Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:02.24,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}私よ燃えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:10.66,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}燃えて抱きしめてみるのは罪じゃないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:17.64,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}火で闇を祓え CHOIR JAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:23.21,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}嘆いても夢は唄わない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:29.23,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}此所で叫んだよ「答えは誰が持ってるの？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:33.70,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}俯いたままじゃ気付かない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:39.95,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}君の瞳の中　未来を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:45.19,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}もしも奇跡が今を指すなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:47.91,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}にじむ涙ぬぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:50.45,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}前を向いて歩こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:55.28,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}私を開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:02:00.99,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}こんな苦しさで何も見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:06.09,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}私よ燃えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:14.12,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}燃えて彼方へ　情熱は罪じゃないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:21.35,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}火で闇を祓え CHOIR JAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:02.24,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}烈焰啊 燃尽我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:10.66,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}想用熊熊燃烧的胸怀抱紧你 这不是罪孽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:17.64,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}用烈焰驱散黑暗 CHOIR JAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:23.21,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}自哀之人怎能唱出梦想之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:29.23,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}站在原地嘶吼“到底谁能给我答案？”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:33.70,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}抬起头来才能察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:39.95,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}你的瞳孔中有着我寻觅已久的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:45.19,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}如果奇迹指向这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:47.91,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}拭去盈眶的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:50.45,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}向前大步前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:55.28,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}解放我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:02:00.99,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}在如此的炼狱中会迷失前进的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:06.09,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}烈焰啊 燃尽我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:14.12,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}化为一道烈焰逝向彼方 这浑身的炙热不是罪孽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:21.35,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}用烈焰驱散黑暗 CHOIR JAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:16.23,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ひとりきりのさびしさ　ひとときのほほえみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:24.17,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたがくれるものは　みんないとしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:33.86,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,すぐそばにいても　触れられないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:42.76,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,心は月のように　形をかえていくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:51.32,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,かなわない約束も　かわかない涙も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:23:02.25,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたがくれたものは　だきしめておどる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:16.23,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人的孤独 一时间的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:24.17,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你为我带来的瑰宝 一样样都令人爱不释手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:33.86,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕两人之间的距离触手可及 可无形之壁注定你我天人永隔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:42.76,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心宛如明月 阴晴圆缺不断变幻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:51.32,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,约定依旧无法实现 眼泪仍然不愿干涸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:23:02.25,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只能把你给的瑰宝 紧拥怀中蓦然舞起..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小此木 意外地有料啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？没那回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 仔细这么一看还真是..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像庚同学这样苗条型的才出挑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是..是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庚同学 我可以摸摸看你的腿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然你也可以摸摸看我的胸部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便附赠一下臀部也没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝..牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以摸摸看你的腿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪之四 拂晓少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即刻起 开始举行灵异调查部暑假强化合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是庚同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然之间要搞合宿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？这..这个嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校的夏夜出现一两个灵异现象是理所当然的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这都不去进行调查 那还算什么灵异调查部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是晚上要住在学校里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:02:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕了吗？新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我倒没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你没关系吧 庚同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前你也一个人就哭了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是不太擅长应付这种吓人的东西吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..我说过那是不可抗力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是天黑脚陂动弹不得而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和新谷同学一起进行合宿真是令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是灵异调查部的强化合宿到底是要强化什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是关于怪谈的真相吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是夕子学姐吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是这个学园最有名的怪谈呢 新谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 说得对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个了不起的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要从哪里入手调查？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间可是多得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人期待呢 新谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是旧值夜室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们睡觉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 榻榻米耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是学校方面居然能点头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明明是个非正式的社团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么啦 只要拜托奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多数的问题都可以解决啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我泡茶了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到值夜一定要面包和茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从水龙头里流出了血！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 新谷同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵异现象这么快就出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是太久不用水管生锈了而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要多放一会水就会变干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不是灵异现象感觉有点遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了啊 夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞一~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的感觉的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有值夜日记耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好旧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪个年头的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敲击门板的声音又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:04:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咚咚 咚咚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门板被强烈的敲击着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前天也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为有人来而开门一看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而门前一定是空无一人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可如果不开门一直放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么敲击门板的声音会变得愈见强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这个学校有着不属于这个世界的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值夜室的怪谈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚真是令人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好..好哇 从日落了就开始认真调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们把夏夜的校舍调查个水落石出吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那..为什么是游泳池？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包场啊包场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要感谢庚同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不..我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为灵异现象的调查要晚上才正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白天还是养精蓄锐一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所..所以我穿了件新泳衣来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好看吗 新谷同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？有这么不合身吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:07.89,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,痛！好痛..痛痛..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！我看上去是如此地痛心疾首吗！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！好痛..请别这样..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 别这样穿比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太华丽了点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小此木同学 你误会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 很合身啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同情反而更显残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我去重新换过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下 小此木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊 夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是被她误会了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哦 新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 新谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看球！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷同学 球过来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们上吧 新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我留在这里是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为值夜室的幽灵说不定会出没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按恐怖电影的设定单独行动的人会最先碰到灵异现象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可第一个牺牲的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像..气氛越来越像了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然..不这样的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我还挺意外的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为庚同学会不太喜欢合宿之类的活动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了吧 我要寻找幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵的话不是有一个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是夕子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个学园里说不定有其他的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:08:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我头一回见到她的时候 夕子也是和现在一样的相貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我也不认为夕子是恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我看见了 影子..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它出现在日没之后的校舍中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被愤怒和憎恨扭曲的恶灵之影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到它之后我就错以为夕子露出了真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在那以后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我眼中的夕子开始变成那副阴森恐怖的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那是因为我内心的主观因素所致
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子并非就是那个恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我所看到的那个阴森恐怖的样子到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个学园里确实存在着恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前因为孤身一人所以只能一味逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在..有了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你 新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,助我一臂之力..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到哪里去了 新谷？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞一是个笨蛋..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多天一直把我撇在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..因为一直是暑假嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为终于把你盼来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果你却只和大家玩在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了我的泳衣也毫无表示
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不关心我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我只有贞一了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过雾江同学也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也能看见夕子学姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算看得见 她也不肯接触我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 贞一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们好久没触碰到彼此了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过..平时都是我主动所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶诶？夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且第一次是贞一主动来触摸我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是..这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么地方都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是你想要的..就算是第一次触摸到的地方也..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那..那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就手吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什..什么事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？机会是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就摸手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由贞一来握住我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞一！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的哭起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个..对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然让你变成孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为人突然消失了 吓了我一跳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾..雾江同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:11:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小此木同学不会睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敲门叫醒她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什..什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成..是值夜室的幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是过去的日记上记载的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一到晚上 不属于这个世界的东西会巡游此地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷 从外面的窗户进去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小此木同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才值夜室的幽灵出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咚咚咚咚敲个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我这个单独行动者差点就成了第一个牺牲者了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值夜室的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:12:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩纸牌吧纸牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵似乎不喜欢到气氛活跃的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶~是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 玩抽鬼牌行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？为什么要发四人份的牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然啦 因为有四个人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我加上新谷加上小此木加上..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啊！！房间里不止三人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡不着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵是睡不着的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是值夜日记吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前啊 我经常来这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了冬天很冷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个房间有暖炉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人可以看见夕子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:14:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 因为敲门的话会以为外面有人而开门嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就趁机进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是重复几次之后 就没有人为我开门了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为打开门也没人在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后光是敲门就会使大家害怕起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这里记载的事情都是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到现在才想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听了老掉牙的往事就想睡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 贞一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谜团这种东西一旦解开就失去了特殊之处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的记忆一旦回忆起来也尽是些平凡琐事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了那种东西而要破坏现在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒石？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕..夕子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵不是睡不着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是睡不着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过可以陪人入睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到外面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？这么晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日没之后意外地凉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想啊 因为这个学校是建在山上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算夏天也有点凉凉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人 偷跑出去想要干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么？怎么干？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男孩子当然抵挡不住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底差在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是想一想就能变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发..要留长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞一 你知道诅咒石吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒石？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那颗石头上刻上怨恨的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能降下诅咒并杀死那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果找到的那个石头上刻着自己的名字的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会因诅咒而死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个学园里似乎有这种石头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旧校舍的内院中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是这个学校的老师找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那个老师遭到了石头的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了逃避石头的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个老师辞了职
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事件全记载在了这个日记上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒石的怪谈..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要调查看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上再说嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就想查清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 我们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 死路？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前是上得去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过之后因为改建而被封死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以从那边跳到隔壁的校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐 危险 前面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁校舍的屋顶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下 夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里要从哪里过去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只是单纯的死路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想跑过来看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要从窗户？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只能从窗户进去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是旧校舍的内院哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被长廊所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按值夜日记记载
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的某处有诅咒石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 就是那块石头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面写着什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个..全部是人名？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面刻上名字就能杀死对方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而发现石头上面刻着自己的名字的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会因诅咒而死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是..诅咒石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒石上..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷贞一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被诅咒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁做出这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办..这样下去的话我会被咒杀而死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是为了这种恶作剧才把我叫醒的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何啊 感觉死得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒这种东西 并不存在于现实中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过..能让人觉得不寒而栗 这本身可能就是诅咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞一也来游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但..但是 现在没穿泳衣..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说值夜日记的老师遭到了诅咒一定也只是人的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定他暗暗知道谁会诅咒他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这种小事就辞职了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人无法发现自己对事物的相信与否根本无从掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无意间相信的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒的力量就会在此萌芽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 虽然诅咒石真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那是借口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开不开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:20:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深夜的散步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想让你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让贞一看一看这个学园的另一番面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然天色越来越浅..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却总让人觉得夜明时分似乎永远不会来临的..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段美好的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不可思议呢 之前我想都没想过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚明明总是这么转瞬而逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是因为贞一发现了我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 贞一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿衣镜中..显出的美艳之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忌避所产生的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深爱着你的我
